#: /opt/splunk/etc/apps/cylance_protect/local/data/ui/views/About.xml:13
msgid ""
"<p>The CylancePROTECT App for Splunk is designed to ingest, parse, and "
"normalize data from the cloud-based Cylance Tenant.  This allows "
"organizations to correlate data using Splunk for a single pane of glass "
"experience.  This application can accept data from either (or both) of "
"the following Cylance Tenant data sources:</p><ul><li>Real-time syslog "
"data <b>(preferred)</b>\n"
"          </li><li>Once per day Threat Data Report (TDR) pulls "
"<b>(optional)</b>\n"
"          </li></ul><p><a "
"href=\"/app/cylance_protect/About?earliest=0&amp;latest=&amp;tour=cylance\">Click"
" here to take a slideshow tour with a brief introduction to the "
"app.</a></p>"
